  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Mathematical Chain showcase emphasizing the Entropy-to-Quantum path. OUROBOROS in Hopf bifurcation topology creates a quasi-periodic oscillation. Entropy Cooler at Stability 0.6 (mild ordering) and CoolRate 0.5 gently shapes the spectral distribution. Quantum Smear at Observation 0.25 and Feedback 0.65 creates a long, smeared reverb tail that blurs the Hopf oscillation into an entangled mass of decaying echos — mathematically ordered (Entropy Cooler) but spectrally uncertain (Quantum Smear). Voronoi Shatter minimal. Attractor Drive at Bifurcation 0.4 (stable, mild saturation). This preset demonstrates the Entropy+Quantum combination that is the chain's most musically useful pairing.",
